  "Covers the heart": "覆盖心脏",
  "Lines the abdominal cavity": "腹腔线",
  "The parietal pleura is the outer layer of the pleural membrane that lines the inner wall of the thoracic cavity. Parietal always refers to the layer attached to the body wall, while visceral refers to the layer on the organ.": "Parietal 胸膜是胸膜的外层,在胸腔的内壁上划线。 Parietal 总是指与身体壁相连的层,而内侧是指器官上的层。",
