  "On the opposite side of the body": "在身体的对面",
  "Ipsilateral means on the same side of the body (ipsi- = same, lateral = side). For example, the right hand and right foot are ipsilateral structures because they are both on the right side.": "例如,右手和右脚是多边结构,因为它们都位于右侧。",
