  "What is the peritoneum?": "腹膜是什么?",
  "The membrane covering the brain": "脑膜覆盖脑膜",
  "The serous membrane surrounding the lungs": "肺部周围的铁膜",
  "The serous membrane lining the abdominopelvic cavity and covering abdominal organs": "腹腔骨盆结膜膜,覆盖腹部器官。",
  "The serous membrane surrounding the heart": "心脏周围的铁膜",
  "The peritoneum is the serous membrane of the abdominopelvic cavity. The visceral peritoneum covers the abdominal organs, while the parietal peritoneum lines the abdominal wall, with peritoneal fluid between them reducing friction.": "腹膜是腹腔骨盆腔的铁皮膜。内脏腹膜覆盖腹部器官,而腹膜腹部膜则在腹部壁上划线,中间有腹膜液,减少摩擦。",
