  "The patellar region is the anterior (front) surface of the knee, named after the patella (kneecap). The patellar reflex (knee-jerk reflex) is tested in this region during neurological examinations.": "Patellar区域是膝盖的前部(前部)表面,以patella(膝盖)命名,在这一区域,在神经检查中测试了Patellar反射(膝部-乳部反射)。",
