  "The plantar region refers to the sole (bottom surface) of the foot. Plantar fasciitis, a common cause of heel pain, involves inflammation of the thick band of connective tissue on the plantar surface.": "Plantar地区指脚的唯一(地表下),Plantar Fasciitis是导致脚跟疼痛的一个常见原因,它涉及板块表面厚厚的连接组织带炎。",
