  "The buttock area": "臀部区域",
  "The gluteal region refers to the buttock area, named after the gluteal muscles (gluteus maximus, medius, and minimus). Intramuscular injections are often administered in this region.": "谷类区域指以谷类肌肉命名的臀部区域(格鲁特斯最大肌肉、梅迪乌斯和微型肌肉),肌肉内注射通常在这一地区进行。",
