  "The antecubital region (antecubital fossa) is the shallow depression on the anterior surface of the elbow (ante- = before, cubital = elbow). It is the standard site for drawing blood (venipuncture) and measuring blood pressure.": "前比特区(antubitial fossa)是肘部前部表面的浅度低压(ante-= before, citbitial = elbital = 肘部),是抽血(venbital fossa)和测量血压的标准场所。",
  "What does 'visceral' mean when describing a serous membrane?": "在描述一个忧郁膜时,“螺旋”意味着什么?",
  "The layer that lines the body wall": "将体壁划线的层层",
  "A membrane that produces mucus": "产生粘膜的膜",
  "A membrane found only in the brain": "脑中只发现脑膜膜",
  "The layer that directly covers the surface of an organ": "直接覆盖器官表面的层层",
  "Visceral refers to the layer of a serous membrane that is directly adhered to the surface of an organ (viscus = organ). For example, the visceral pleura covers the lungs, and the visceral pericardium covers the heart.": "子宫是指直系于器官表面(视网膜=器官)的细胞膜层。例如,内膜胸膜覆盖肺部,内膜心肌膜覆盖心脏。",
  "What does 'parietal' mean when describing a serous membrane?": "在描述一种硅膜时,“帕雷塔”意味着什么?",
  "The layer directly covering an organ": "直接覆盖一个机关的层层",
  "A membrane found only around the brain": "脑中只有脑膜",
  "The layer lining the wall of a body cavity": "体洞的壁上,有一层层,有一层层,有一层层,有一层层,有一层层,有一层层,有一层层,有一层层,有一层层,有一层层,有一层层,有一层层,有一层层,有一层层,",
  "A layer that produces blood cells": "产生血细胞的层层",
  "Parietal refers to the layer of a serous membrane that lines the wall of a body cavity (paries = wall). For example, the parietal pleura lines the thoracic wall, and the parietal peritoneum lines the abdominal wall.": "Parietal 指在身体腔壁上划线的细胞膜层(Parietal ) 。 例如, Parietal 胸膜线、胸壁和腹膜线。",
  "What does 'abdominopelvic quadrant' mean?": "\"baddominopelvic quarent\"是什么意思?",
  "A division of the thoracic cavity into four parts": "将胸腔分为四部分",
  "A method of dividing the body into left and right halves": "将身体分为左右两半的方法",
  "One of nine regions used to divide the abdomen": "曾经分割腹部的九个地区之一",
  "One of four sections created by dividing the abdominopelvic region with one vertical and one horizontal line through the umbilicus": "将腹腹骨切片区分为一条垂直线和一条横直线,通过伦比利丘斯划分成一条垂直线和一条水平线,由此建立的四个区之一。",
  "The four abdominopelvic quadrants (RUQ, LUQ, RLQ, LLQ) are created by drawing one vertical and one horizontal line through the umbilicus (navel), dividing the abdominopelvic area into four sections used clinically to describe the location of pain, organs, and pathology.": "4个腹腔骨盆(RUQ、LUQ、RLQ、LLQ、LLQ)是通过通过伦比利丘斯(navil)绘制一条垂直和一条水平线,将腹腔骨盆分为4个部分,临床用于描述疼痛、器官和病理的位置。",
  "A patient arrives at the emergency room complaining of severe pain in their lower right abdomen. The physician suspects appendicitis. Using anatomical terminology, the pain is located in the:": "病人到达急诊室,抱怨右下腹部有严重疼痛。医生怀疑有天体炎。用解剖术语,疼痛位于:",
  "Left upper quadrant (LUQ)": "左上方象限( LUQ)",
  "Left lower quadrant (LLQ)": "左下方格( LLQ)",
  "Right lower quadrant (RLQ)": "右下象限( RLQ)",
  "Right upper quadrant (RUQ)": "右上方象限( RUQ)",
  "Appendicitis pain typically localizes to the right lower quadrant (RLQ) because the appendix is attached to the cecum in this region. The specific point of maximum tenderness is called McBurney's point, located one-third of the way from the right anterior superior iliac spine to the umbilicus.": "腹膜炎疼痛一般都与右下方象限(RLQ)相对应,因为附录附在这一地区的蓄积上,最大体温的具体点叫做McBurney的点,从右侧前脊椎到伦比丘的距离为三分之一。",
  "A nurse is documenting that a patient has a rash on the front of both knees. Using correct anatomical terminology, she should describe the rash as being on the _____ region bilaterally.": "一名护士正在记录病人双膝前部有皮疹。 她应该使用正确的解剖术语,将皮疹描述为双边地区。",
  "Patellar": "帕特列尔",
  "Crural": "农村 农村",
  "Popliteal": "流行",
  "Femoral": "女性",
  "The patellar region refers to the anterior (front) surface of the knee. Bilateral means on both sides. The popliteal region would refer to the back of the knee, while the femoral region is the thigh.": "角形区域指膝盖的前部(前部)表面,两侧的双边手段。 角形区域指膝后部,而侧形区域指大腿。",
  "A phlebotomist (blood-draw technician) is looking for a suitable vein to draw blood. She ties a tourniquet on the patient's upper arm and palpates the area at the inner bend of the elbow. This anatomical area is the:": "一位血吸技术员(phlebotomist)正在寻找合适的血管来抽血。 她将止血带绑在病人的上臂上,然后在手肘的内弯处转动。 这个解剖区是:",
