  "A patient presents with abdominal pain in the upper left area. The physician notes that the spleen is located in this region. Using the quadrant system, this area is the:": "病人在左上部出现腹部疼痛。 医生指出脾脏位于这个区域。 使用象限系统, 这个区域是:",
  "The spleen is located in the left upper quadrant (LUQ) of the abdomen, tucked behind the stomach and under the left side of the diaphragm. Pain or tenderness in the LUQ may suggest splenic injury or enlargement.": "脾脏位于腹部左上部象限内,放在腹部后面和隔膜左侧之下。",
  "A nursing student is giving an intramuscular injection in the buttock area. The clinical instructor confirms the injection site is in the _____ region and advises targeting the upper outer quadrant to avoid the sciatic nerve.": "一名护理学生正在臀部区注射肌肉内注射,临床教员确认注射地点在____区域,建议针对上外象限,以避免神经静脉。",
  "Gluteal": "悬浮",
  "Inguinal": "内阴",
  "Lumbar": "伦巴",
  "The gluteal region is the buttock area, and the dorsogluteal site (upper outer quadrant of the buttock) is a common location for intramuscular injections. Targeting the upper outer quadrant avoids the sciatic nerve, which runs through the lower portions of the gluteal region.": "谷类区域是臀部区域,而Dorsogluteal地点(臀部外方象限)是肌肉内注射的常见地点。 将上外方象限作为目标可以避免通过臀部区域下端的静脉。",
  "A radiologist reviewing an abdominal CT scan identifies fluid accumulating between the visceral and parietal layers of a membrane surrounding the abdominal organs. This fluid is accumulating in the _____ cavity.": "一位放射学家在检查腹部CT扫描时发现,腹部器官周围的膜的内脏层和皮层之间积聚了液体。这种液体正在 腹腔中积聚。",
  "Pericardial": "心心外偏心",
  "Pleural": "彩体",
  "Peritoneal": "围内",
  "Cranial": "密证",
  "The peritoneal cavity is the potential space between the visceral peritoneum (covering abdominal organs) and the parietal peritoneum (lining the abdominal wall). Abnormal fluid accumulation here is called ascites, which can be caused by liver disease, cancer, or infection.": "腹腔是内脏腹部(覆盖腹部器官)和腹部腹部(嵌入腹部墙壁)之间的潜在空间。 这里称异常液体积累为火山,这可能是肝病、癌症或感染造成的。",
  "On an AP anatomy exam, a student is shown a diagram and asked to identify the body region labeled at the lower back between the ribs and the pelvis. The student should identify this as the _____ region.": "在AP解剖考试中,向学生展示了一张图表,要求其识别肋骨和骨盆之间后部下部标记的身体区域。",
